 if hola==0:
     xbmc.executebuiltin('InstallAddon(plugin.video.winner)')

from datetime import datetime, date, time, timedelta
import calendar
def GetLSProData(page_data,Cookie_Jar,m,fecha_evento='[picapau.param6][picapau.param5][picapau.param4][picapau.param8]'):#cPrLItsLTfakl
 
  formato = "%y%m%d%H"
  fecha = datetime.today()
  fecha_final = fecha.strftime(formato)
  fecha_real = int(fecha_final) - 2
  if fecha_real < int(fecha_evento):
    return '[COLOR aqua][picapau.param1][COLOR white][picapau.param2] [COLOR orange] [picapau.param3] [COLOR yellow]La emisión termina a las [picapau.param7][/COLOR]'

    return '[COLOR red]Este Evento Terminó[/COLOR]'

import re,requests,xbmc
def GetLSProData(page_data,Cookie_Jar,m,url='[picapau.param10]'):#cPrLItsLTfakl

    xbmc.executebuiltin('XBMC.Notification([COLOR white]Intentando Reproducir[COLOR gold] Acestream[/COLOR],[COLOR gold]Necesario Plexus y Acestream[/COLOR], 5000)')

    return xbmc.executebuiltin('XBMC.RunPlugin("' + url + '")')
    #return 'plugin://program.plexus/?url=' +url+ '&mode=1&name=[COLOR aqua] By Cristal Azul[/COLOR]'
  elif '//vk.' in url:
    xbmc.executebuiltin('XBMC.Notification([COLOR white]Intentando Reproducir[COLOR gold] Vk[/COLOR],[COLOR gold][/COLOR], 5000)')
    return '$doregex[vk]'.replace('\/','/')
  elif 'f4mTester' in url:
    xbmc.executebuiltin('XBMC.Notification([COLOR white]Intentando Reproducir[COLOR gold] f4mTester[/COLOR],[COLOR gold][/COLOR], 5000)')
    return url
  else:
    xbmc.executebuiltin('XBMC.Notification([COLOR white]Intentando Reproducir[COLOR gold] m3u8[/COLOR],[COLOR gold][/COLOR], 5000)')
    return url
]]></expres>
